Welcome to TestiFi - a tool to help you put your story into words

Don't worry about having all your thoughts together. Simply share your story, one piece at a time, and I'll do the rest. 

This tool is in early development, so it may have some hiccups. Your feedback will help make it better, and all shared information stays confidential.

Let's have a conversation about how you met Jesus. What was your life like before you came to know Christ?
